Plifk,is,a,service,that,allows,users,to,upload,and,share,their,files,on,the,Internet,Upon,signup,users,get,a,Plifk,URL,where,their,files,will,appear,An,API,is,available,that,lets,developers,integrate,some,of,the,service,s,functionality,into,third,party,applications,Available,methods,include,retrieving,user,information,listing,user,tags,retrieving,file,information,and,listing,files,belonging,to,a,user,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON